Package: ayao.hidedoubaopip
Name: HideDoubaoPiP
Version: 0.0.2
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Hide only Doubao IME PiP floating window while preserving normal video PiP. Changes from early v2: removes broad SBPIPPegasusAdapter matching, uses conservative multi-signal Doubao detection, avoids hidden=YES, adds PiP internal layout triggers, and release builds do not write log files.
Maintainer: ayao
Author: ayao
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
